{{Quote|Glass omens, dread crowns, three princesses, shadow lady, deathless is the seeker.|Information about Nintra gleaned by ''[[legend lore|divination magic]]''.}}

As an archfey of the Gloaming Court, Nintra Siotta wielded great power and magical abilities associated with shadows and [[illusion]] magic.

In addition to her spellcasting and spell-like powers, Nintra could conjure forth [[humanoid]] warriors whose bodies were composed of shadow glass.
